{
  "chapter": 16,
  "chapter_summary": "陆小凤独自驾小艇重返神秘海岛，途中反复思念沙曼，但随即进入战斗分析状态。他推理想出崔诚密室杀人案的关键在于“隐形人”，认为只有隐形人才能穿过五道铁栅门的密室。登岛后与小老头重逢，小老头坦承珠宝已被宫九运走、岛上高手已散，直言想让陆小凤接班，陆小凤婉拒加入。小老头对陆小凤的智慧和重诺品格赞赏有加，两人喝酒聊天后，陆小凤乘船离开海岛。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_wu_ming",
      "text": "你的出现，总是那么突如其来？",
      "tone": "惊叹",
      "chapter": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "小老头",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你上次在这个岛上看到的事，你认为很怪异？",
      "tone": "平和",
      "chapter": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_wu_ming",
      "text": "怪异极了。",
      "tone": "肯定",
      "chapter": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "小老头",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "这个岛是不是很神秘？",
      "tone": "平和",
      "chapter": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_wu_ming",
      "text": "神秘极了。",
      "tone": "肯定",
      "chapter": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "小老头",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我是这个岛上的主人。",
      "tone": "自信",
      "chapter": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_wu_ming",
      "text": "所以你理所当然的透着神秘？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "小老头",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "一点不错。",
      "tone": "肯定",
      "chapter": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_wu_ming",
      "text": "你知道我这次重回岛上，有什么目的？",
      "tone": "试探",
      "chapter": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "小老头",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我当然知道，你有很多疑问，需要我给你答案。",
      "tone": "自信",
      "chapter": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_wu_ming",
      "text": "你会给我答案吗？",
      "tone": "追问",
      "chapter": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "小老头",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你看呢？",
      "tone": "反问",
      "chapter": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_wu_ming",
      "text": "会。",
      "tone": "肯定",
      "chapter": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "小老头",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_wu_ming",
      "text": "以你的武功，以你的智慧，你根本不必隐瞒任何事。",
      "tone": "奉承",
      "chapter": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "小老头",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你说得很对，只是我却另外有一个希望。",
      "tone": "诚恳",
      "chapter": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_wu_ming",
      "text": "什么希望？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "小老头",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我希望你是回来告诉我一件事。",
      "tone": "期待",
      "chapter": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_wu_ming",
      "text": "什么事？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "小老头",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你愿意加入我这一行。",
      "tone": "期待",
      "chapter": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_wu_ming",
      "text": "我只有让你失望了。",
      "tone": "歉意",
      "chapter": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "小老头",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我知道。",
      "tone": "理解",
      "chapter": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_wu_ming",
      "text": "你怎么知道？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "小老头",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "因为你是一个人回来的。",
      "tone": "洞察",
      "chapter": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_wu_ming",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "小老头",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "如果你要加入我这一行，你就会带着沙曼回来。可是你并没有。",
      "tone": "解释",
      "chapter": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "小老头",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我希望我的失望是暂时的。",
      "tone": "感叹",
      "chapter": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_wu_ming",
      "text": "对于你的希望，我很抱歉不能给你任何诺言。",
      "tone": "歉意",
      "chapter": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "小老头",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我知道。",
      "tone": "理解",
      "chapter": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_wu_ming",
      "text": "你又知道？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "小老头",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "因为你不是别人，你是陆小凤。陆小凤是最重诺言的。",
      "tone": "赞赏",
      "chapter": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "小老头",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你能够逃过宫九在船上的攻击，我相信，你的智慧，绝对比我高，我相信，你对于那批珠宝失窃的事，一定想出了很多线索。",
      "tone": "赞赏",
      "chapter": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_wu_ming",
      "text": "我只知道一件事。",
      "tone": "谨慎",
      "chapter": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "小老头",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "哪一件？",
      "tone": "追问",
      "chapter": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_wu_ming",
      "text": "窃案是你策划的，珠宝和失踪的人都在岛上。",
      "tone": "断言",
      "chapter": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "小老头",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你说对了一半。",
      "tone": "肯定",
      "chapter": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_wu_ming",
      "text": "哪一半？",
      "tone": "追问",
      "chapter": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "小老头",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "前面的一半。",
      "tone": "肯定",
      "chapter": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_wu_ming",
      "text": "你是说，珠宝和人已经不在岛上？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "小老头",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "不错。",
      "tone": "肯定",
      "chapter": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_wu_ming",
      "text": "宫九已经把珠宝和人运回去？",
      "tone": "追问",
      "chapter": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "小老头",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "人，宫九另有打算。珠宝，总是要花掉的。",
      "tone": "解释",
      "chapter": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_wu_ming",
      "text": "他一个人怎么花？",
      "tone": "追问",
      "chapter": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "小老头",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "不是一个人，是很多人。",
      "tone": "肯定",
      "chapter": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_wu_ming",
      "text": "怪不得这里的人一个也不剩，原来他们都去花这笔钱去了。",
      "tone": "恍然",
      "chapter": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "小老头",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "所以，我心目中理想的接班人，只有一个。",
      "tone": "期待",
      "chapter": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_wu_ming",
      "text": "谁？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "小老头",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你！",
      "tone": "坚定",
      "chapter": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_wu_ming",
      "text": "为什么只有我？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "小老头",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "因为他们都不能甘于寂寞。大吃大喝大玩大闹的人，是很容易被人控制的人。",
      "tone": "解释",
      "chapter": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_wu_ming",
      "text": "对你来说，这不是很理想吗？",
      "tone": "反问",
      "chapter": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "小老头",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "是很理想，只是，我也就很寂寞了。",
      "tone": "感叹",
      "chapter": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_wu_ming",
      "text": "因为你找不到接你的班，做领导的人？",
      "tone": "理解",
      "chapter": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "小老头",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "所以，我很喜欢你。",
      "tone": "真诚",
      "chapter": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "小老头",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你对这件窃案，有什么疑问？",
      "tone": "询问",
      "chapter": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_wu_ming",
      "text": "以你们的人力和武功，我知道，要窃去这批珠宝，是轻而易举的事。所以，我只有一个问题想不透。",
      "tone": "分析",
      "chapter": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "小老头",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "哪一个问题？",
      "tone": "追问",
      "chapter": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_wu_ming",
      "text": "崔诚的死。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "小老头",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "记得我对你说过的隐形人吗？",
      "tone": "反问",
      "chapter": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_wu_ming",
      "text": "我的意思是，杀崔诚的人，是怎么隐形的？",
      "tone": "追问",
      "chapter": 16
    }
  ],
